Haskell V. Anderson III https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Haskell_V._Anderson_III 0 Haskell Vaughn Anderson III is an American film, television and theater actor. He is most known for his prominent supporting role in the 1989 film Kickboxer, which starred Jean-Claude Van Damme. Other Independent Film Star roles include the 1978 film Brotherhood of Death, which was his first starring role on film and the 2007 Independent feature Boy and Dog.
